channel.description:
Lol I just thought about a little place right here were youc an post some pics you think are funny (no porn..no things with sex.. if my parents see ill never get on comp again, guessing..)just post what you think is funny.. pics, jokes...umm.. puns i dunno just post funny stuffs here :)[br][size=1]Posted on: December 28, 2006, 09:09:08 PM[/size][hr]I will start off
A guy is walking on the beach and he see's a a plastic bottle he picked it up and said man..im thirsty so he rubbed the bottle and a genie came out and the genie said ok you get three wishes, and the man says ok my first one is i wish i had a mansion! and the genie said ok, and the man had a motor home and he said what.. i said a mansion.. and the genie said whatever you wish for your parents get half of it, and the man said.. that sucks... so then the genie said next wish? and the man said i wish I was rich, and the genie granted it and the genie gave 1milion dollars but his parents got 900,000 dollars, and the man said why do i only get that much? and the genie said, i'm sorry ur parents get 75% of it not half my appologies, then the man says ok I wish...You beat me up half to death.
